[
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "8 inches up top overnight, wind loaded the lee side of No Name Chute pretty hard.",
    "thread_ts": "1769882891.000000",
    "ts": "1769882891.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Saw the plot. You thinking control work before we open it?",
    "thread_ts": "1769882891.000000",
    "ts": "1769882891.000001",
    "user_id": "U002JAKE"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Yeah. Grabbing charges at 0600, want you on the ridge with me.",
    "thread_ts": "1769882891.000000",
    "ts": "1769882891.000002",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "I'm in. Tanner sign off on opening it yet?",
    "thread_ts": "1769882891.000000",
    "ts": "1769882891.000003",
    "user_id": "U002JAKE"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Not yet, sending him the stability numbers now.",
    "thread_ts": "1769882891.000000",
    "ts": "1769882891.000004",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Cool. Meet at the shack or up top?",
    "thread_ts": "1769882891.000000",
    "ts": "1769882891.000005",
    "user_id": "U002JAKE"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Shack, 0545. Bring your spare radio, mine's acting up again.",
    "thread_ts": "1769882891.000000",
    "ts": "1769882891.000006",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Copy that. See you in the dark.",
    "thread_ts": "1769882891.000000",
    "ts": "1769882891.000007",
    "user_id": "U002JAKE"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Got 14 inches overnight up top. Rendezvous Bowl still soft slab on the lee side, wanna go dig a pit before we call it?",
    "thread_ts": "1769801326.000000",
    "ts": "1769801326.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Yeah I'm free till 8. Meet at the Bridger junction?",
    "thread_ts": "1769801326.000000",
    "ts": "1769801326.000001",
    "user_id": "U003MARK"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Works. Bring the extra probe, mine's still drying out from yesterday.",
    "thread_ts": "1769801326.000000",
    "ts": "1769801326.000002",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Ha, noted. Tanner's asking if we can have a green light by 9 for dispatch.",
    "thread_ts": "1769801326.000000",
    "ts": "1769801326.000003",
    "user_id": "U003MARK"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Doable if the pit's clean. If not I'm not signing off just to hit his clock.",
    "thread_ts": "1769801326.000000",
    "ts": "1769801326.000004",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Agreed, safety over schedule, always. I'll radio dispatch to hold.",
    "thread_ts": "1769801326.000000",
    "ts": "1769801326.000005",
    "user_id": "U003MARK"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Appreciate it. See you at Bridger, 7:15.",
    "thread_ts": "1769801326.000000",
    "ts": "1769801326.000006",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Copy that. Bringing coffee, you're buying next round at the Mangy Moose.",
    "thread_ts": "1769801326.000000",
    "ts": "1769801326.000007",
    "user_id": "U003MARK"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Dave, checking on the compressed air canister order for our airbags. Jake Tanner wants em in hand before September.",
    "thread_ts": "1769649855.000000",
    "ts": "1769649855.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Yeah sorry Jeff, supplier pushed us to Aug 12. Sixty units still good?",
    "thread_ts": "1769649855.000000",
    "ts": "1769649855.000001",
    "user_id": "U004DAVE"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Sixty works. Can you split shipment, half to the patrol shack half to my house? Don't want em sitting in the truck bay.",
    "thread_ts": "1769649855.000000",
    "ts": "1769649855.000002",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Can do. Also heads up, price went up 4% since spring quote.",
    "thread_ts": "1769649855.000000",
    "ts": "1769649855.000003",
    "user_id": "U004DAVE"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Fine, just get me the updated PO and I'll get Jake's signature.",
    "thread_ts": "1769649855.000000",
    "ts": "1769649855.000004",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Sending it now. Still running that same billing address on Cache St?",
    "thread_ts": "1769649855.000000",
    "ts": "1769649855.000005",
    "user_id": "U004DAVE"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Yep, same one. Appreciate you chasing the manufacturer on this.",
    "thread_ts": "1769649855.000000",
    "ts": "1769649855.000006",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "No problem. I'll call you when they clear customs.",
    "thread_ts": "1769649855.000000",
    "ts": "1769649855.000007",
    "user_id": "U004DAVE"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
    "text": "Got 14 inches overnight up top, wind loaded hard on the north side of Rendezvous Bowl",
    "thread_ts": "1769539372.000000",
    "ts": "1769539372.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": 0,
